csdl.jupiter.util
Class ResourceBundleKey

java.lang.Object
  csdl.jupiter.util.ResourceBundleKey

public class ResourceBundleKey
extends java.lang.Object

Provides the keys in the resource bundle. Used as constant value if the keys are supposed to embedded in a source code. The main purpose of this is for the maintenance to reduce the cost to replace resource bundle key if they are supposed to be changed.

Version:
$Id: ResourceBundleKey.java,v 1.12 2005/03/25 18:32:07 takuyay Exp $
Author:
Takuya Yamashita
